                        <interp inst="t18400511-name-1160" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS COLSON</persName>
                  </hi>. I am the superintendent of the works of the London and Croydon Railway. This lead was cut from a house which is the pro<lb></lb>perty of the company—I produce the Act of Parliament which constitutes the Londonand Croydon Railway Company a corporate body.</p>
